Name: Casual pants
Description0:
The Wild West and the city are just a short step apart. These soft lambskin 5-pocket pants echo classic Texas styling with a contemporary, urban twist. 
Perfect for bold looks bursting with personality, these pants certainly won't go unnoticed. The leather used to make this item was treated in a tannery whose environmental performance is assessed in order to reduce its impact at all stages of the production process.The model is wearing an Italian size S/40
